\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 The twinkling sky above the crater\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s rim was a magnificent blue. The clean air was invigorating. He closed his eyes and took a deep, deep breath. Soreness wrecked his body. It would have bulled him over if he weren\u8217\'92t dwelling in his own periphery.}
